yContaineruniface_104vip1665702725886.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vip1665702725886.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vip1665702725886.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vip1665702725886\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      identifiers\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vip1665702725886__identifiers_145268\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vip1665702725886__topic_d47741e1_d47742e1_d47743e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vip1665702725886__d6532e17\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = identifiers : quoted | unquoted</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vip1665702725886__d6532e26\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = ids: quoted | unquoted</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vip1665702725886__topic_d31207e1_d31208e1_d31209e1_d31210e1_d31211e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227504e74\">\n                        \n Use\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Applies to</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Syntax</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2 connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">MS SQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MSS</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">MySQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MQL</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MQL_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">SQLite connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">SLE</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vip1665702725886__table_d4499e1_d4500e1_d4501e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$SLE_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vip1665702725886__topic_d31212e1_d31213e1_d31214e1_d31215e1_d31216e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227504e215\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vip1665702725886__p_d47756e1_d47757e1_d47758e1\">This option controls whether identifiers such as table names or field names in generated SQL statements will be enclosed in double quotation marks. This is useful when reserved words are used as entity or field names.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vip1665702725886__p_d47759e1_d47760e1_d47761e1\">When this option is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">quoted</code>, all characters can be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vip1665702725886__p_d47762e1_d47763e1_d47764e1\">If this setting is not specified, it defaults to <code class=\"ph codeph\">unquoted</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533035\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533035\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "identifiers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 identifiers Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = identifiers : quoted | unquoted USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = ids: quoted | unquoted Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax DB2 connector DB2 USYS$DB2_PARAMS MS SQL connector MSS USYS$MSS_PARAMS MySQL connector MQL USYS$MQL_PARAMS SQLite connector SLE USYS$SLE_PARAMS Description This option controls whether identifiers such as table names or field names in generated SQL statements will be enclosed in double quotation marks. This is useful when reserved words are used as entity or field names. When this option is set to quoted , all characters can be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs. If this setting is not specified, it defaults to unquoted . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}